<HEADLINE>
<P>
BODY WATCH; WHAT'S THE DEAL; HOW YOU CAN HIDE SOME OF YOUR SPONGY SELF 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By C.A. WEDLAN 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Chaffing terms such as cellulite, uneven, dimpled, bumpy, spongy and 
orange-peel skin are apt to make you feel thigh-shy.Consider the cures: 
</P>
<P>
 * Crinolines from Renee Strauss for the Bride, on Wilshire, $55. 
</P>
