</P>
<P>
 Miami (49-13) advanced to today's elimination game against the loser of Monday 
night's game between Oklahoma and Arizona State. 
</P>
<P>
 Auburn (44-21) was ousted, losing both games in its first CWS appearance since 
1976. 
</P>
<P>
 Miami took advantage of an error for four unearned runs in the first. The 
Hurricanes scored three times in the seventh. 
