<TEXT>
<P>
 Lance Perry of the Orange Coast men's volleyball team, the most valuable 
player of the Orange Empire Conference, has signed with Long Beach State.Perry, 
from Amarillo (Tex.) High School, led OCC in kills with 257 and was selected 
MVP of the State tournament. . . . UC Irvine signed four women's soccer 
players. They are Laurie Wilson of Cypress College, a two-time Orange Empire 
Conference MVP; Tracie Ann Manz from Estancia High, the Pacific Coast League 
MVP; Nicole Kelly from Lakewood High, the Moore League MVP, and Bridget Arnett 
from Torrance Bishop Montgomery High. 
