</P>
<P>
 Sweet, Stanley B., 84, of Moorpark, retired pipe fitter. Pierce Brothers 
Griffin Mortuary, Thousand Oaks. 
</P>
<P>
 Zoller, Dorothy C., 86, of Camarillo, homemaker. Pierce Brothers Griffin 
Mortuary, Camarillo. 
</P>
<P>
 Ventura County obituaries are published free of charge as a public service to 
readers. Obituaries are based on information provided by mortuaries. 
</P>
