<DOCNO> LA060794-0077 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 049040 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 7, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
