<TEXT>
<P>
 Kanan Road between Agoura Road and Tunnel No. 3 in Agoura Hills has been 
slated for either reconstruction or resurfacing in September. 
</P>
<P>
 The project, scheduled to be completed by August, 1995, will involve paving 
dirt shoulders, building guardrails, improving drainage, widening a bridge and 
removing one tree. 
</P>
<P>
 The Los Angeles County Department of Public Works will administer the project, 
which will be funded by Agoura Hills and the county.  
</P>
<P>
 Traffic lanes in the area may be reduced during daytime working hours, but 
local access is expected to be maintained at all other times. MAKI BECKER 
