addressing his troops before battle, Allies' Communique 1 announcing the 
landing in occupied territory, Gen. Dwight D. Eisenhower's message to the 
people of France and President Franklin D. Roosevelt reciting his D-day prayer. 
To hear these recordings, call TimesLink and press * and the four-digit code. 
</P>
<P>
