<P>
 Lawsuits Promised Over Sea Turtle Deaths: U.S. environmental groups and the 
Georgia Fisherman's Assn., a shrimp-fishing trade group, said they will sue the 
federal government, alleging that it failed to make foreign shrimpers as well 
as the U.S. fleet curb practices that cause rare sea turtles to drown. Under 
